rollcalls.description: TO OVERRIDE VETO OF H. R. 10530, (P. A. 643), WHICH EXTENDS FOR TWO ADDITIONAL YEARS THE 31/2% INTEREST RATE ON CERTAIN FEDERAL LAND BANK LOANS, AND PROVIDES FOR A 4% INTEREST RATE ON LAND BANK COMMISIONERS LOANS UNTIL JULY 15, 1940. (P. 6926, COL. 1).
